en antialiased\"><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 bg-black/95 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 border-b border-gray-800\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center py-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-8\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a><div class=\"relative group\"><button class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition flex items-center\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Mahsulotlar<svg class=\"ml-1 w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#portfolio\">Portfolio</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#process\">Jarayon</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 border-l border-gray-700 pl-4\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-gray-400 hover:text-white\" hrefLang=\"ru\" href=\"/ru\">RU</a><span class=\"text-gray-600\">/</span><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-teal-500\" hrefLang=\"uz\" href=\"/uz\">UZ</a></div></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex flex-col items-end space-y-1\"><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-white font-semibold hover:text-teal-500 transition text-sm\">+998 77 080 22 88</a><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-300 text-xs hover:text-teal-500 transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Открыть меню\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"pt-20\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"8 mart sovg'alari: 20 g'oya (korporativ, gravirovka)\",\"description\":\"8 martga jamoa uchun sovg'a tanlang: 20 g'oya, byudjet bo'yicha. Toshkentda lazer gravirovka bilan buyurtma qiling!\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/8-mart-uchun-korporativ-sovgalar-goyalari\",\"image\":\"/images/blog/8-mart-uchun-korporativ-sovgalar-goyalari.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-03\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-03\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/8-mart-uchun-korporativ-sovgalar-goyalari\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"8 mart sovg'alari: 20 g'oya (korporativ, gravirovka)\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/8-mart-uchun-korporativ-sovgalar-goyalari\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">8 mart sovg&#x27;alari: 20 g&#x27;oya (korporativ, gravirovka)</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">8 mart sovg&#x27;alari: 20 g&#x27;oya (korporativ, gravirovka)</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-03-03\">2-mart, 2026</time><span>3<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/8-mart-uchun-korporativ-sovgalar-goyalari.jpg\" alt=\"8 mart sovg&#x27;alari: 20 g&#x27;oya (korporativ, gravirovka)\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>8 martda sovg&#x27;a - bu &quot;e&#x27;tibor&quot;ning eng ko&#x27;rinadigan shakli. B2Bda esa yana bir vazifa bor: hammasi bir xil standartda, tirajda, o&#x27;z vaqtida va brendga mos bo&#x27;lishi. Bu maqolada 20 g&#x27;oya va amaliy tanlov qoidalari.</p>\n<h2>B2B nuqtai nazari: 8 mart sovg&#x27;asining 4 maqsadi</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>E&#x27;tirof va hurmat (jamoa motivatsiyasi)</li>\n<li>Employer brand (ichki PR)</li>\n<li>Standartlashtirilgan jarayon (zakup uchun oson)</li>\n<li>Brendli, ammo elegant ko&#x27;rinish (lazer gravirovka)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Byudjetni qanday tanlash: &quot;kishi boshiga&quot; yondashuv</h2>\n<p>Amaliy tavsiya: 3 paket qiling - byudjet, standart, premium. Shunda bir xil tiraj ichida ham segmentlash oson.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Byudjet: kichik, ammo yoqimli (promo emas)</li>\n<li>Standart: eng balansli, ko&#x27;pchilik uchun</li>\n<li>Premium: rahbarlar/kalit rol egalari uchun</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>20 g&#x27;oya (gravirovka/branding bilan)</h2>\n<p>| # | G&#x27;oya | Brending/gravirovka | Byudjet darajasi |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | Ism gravirovkali termo-krujka | Logo + ism, minimal | Standart/Premium |\n| 2 | Premium ruchka + daftar seti | Ruchkada gravirovka | Standart |\n| 3 | Yog&#x27;och qutida mini-set | Qopqoqda gravirovka | Premium |\n| 4 | Brelok (metal) + karta | Gravirovka, tabrik | Byudjet |\n| 5 | Suv idishi (sport) | Logo + motivatsion so&#x27;z | Standart |\n| 6 | Desk-organayzer | Yog&#x27;ochda gravirovka | Premium |\n| 7 | Kabel/adapter seti (pouch) | Pouch brending | Standart |\n| 8 | Shokolad/snack + tabrik | Qadoqqa stiker | Byudjet |\n| 9 | Kofe/Choy mini-set | Qadoq brending | Standart |\n| 10 | Aroma sham (neytral) | Yorliq brending | Standart |\n| 11 | Mini-kosmetika (care set) | Qadoq brending | Standart |\n| 12 | T-shirt (jamoa merch) | Print | Standart |\n| 13 | Cap/shapkacha | Kashta/print | Byudjet/Standart |\n| 14 | Notbuk stendi | Gravirovka | Premium |\n| 15 | Mousepad | Print/markirovka | Standart |\n| 16 | Planner (2025/2026) | Muqovada gravirovka | Standart |\n| 17 | Metall vizitka qutisi | Gravirovka | Premium |\n| 18 | Zargarlik qutichasi (neytral) | Gravirovka | Premium |\n| 19 | Mini-issiq ichimlik termos | Logo + ism | Premium |\n| 20 | Gullar + brend karta (kombo) | Karta brending | Byudjet/Standart |</p>\n<p><em>Eslatma: Narxlar bo&#x27;yicha yakuniy hisob-kitob tiraj va modelga bog&#x27;liq. Bu yerda byudjet darajasi ko&#x27;rsatilgan.</em></p>\n<h2>Lazer gravirovka: 8 mart uchun eng toza premium effekt</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Haddan tashqari rangli printdan ko&#x27;ra elegantroq</li>\n<li>Metall buyumlarda juda chiroyli ko&#x27;rinadi</li>\n<li>Ism qo&#x27;shilsa - sovg&#x27;a shaxsiylashadi</li>\n<li>Tirajda bir xil sifat saqlanadi</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Muddat va logistika: kechikmaslik uchun</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Eng yaxshi start: 8 martdan 2-3 hafta oldin</li>\n<li>Ro&#x27;yxat: ismlar bo&#x27;lsa, 2 bosqichli tekshiruv</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash: bir xil, ichki tartib bilan</li>\n<li>Yetkazish: ofisga yoki tadbir joyiga aniq sana</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?</strong> Telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/graveruz\">@graveruz</a> ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to&#x27;ldiring.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/rahbar-uchun-8-mart-vip-goya\">Rahbar uchun 8 mart: 10 VIP g&#x27;oya (gravirovka)</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Rahbar uchun statusli sovg&#x27;a tanlang: $50-$500 diapazonda 10 g&#x27;oya. Toshkentda gravirovka bilan buyurtma qiling!</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar 2025: O&#x27;zbekistonda to&#x27;liq gid</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Xodimlar, hamkorlar va mijozlar uchun sovg&#x27;ani to&#x27;g&#x27;ri tanlang. Byudjet, g&#x27;oya, gravirovka. Hisob-kitob so&#x27;rang!</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/catalog-products\">Mahsulotlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Aloqa</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 77 080 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">Telegram</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">Toshkent, Mukimiy ko&#x27;chasi</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8 text-center\"><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Graver.uz. <!-- -->Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan<!-- -->.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-68f22649503f8e75.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1: